link: https://app-twitt-explainer.herokuapp.com
app maked with flask, and a classifier SVM with 78% of accuracy. The interpretation results are guive by LIME Framework.
The app receive a english text about covid from tweet (without #,@, links) and classify the sentiment like positive, neutral or negative and the black-box is (SVM) is
explained and a graph with the more relevants words to the classifier with LIME Framework. The app also run with text of sites about covid.

